'''SoroSuub Transport and Supply Division''' was part of the [[SoroSuub Corporation/Legends|SoroSuub Corporation]]. The division handled SoroSuub's cargo transfer operations, and operated bulk freighters, container ships, and barge drivers such as the [[Nyubba-class cargo barge driver|''Nyubba''-class]].

